## âœ¨ Slackle up your Slack!

[**Slackle**](https://slackle.dev) is a lightweight and magical framework for building Slack apps effortlessly.

[â†’ Visit the Official Website](https://slackle.dev)

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- âš¡ï¸ **Slash command routing** â€” Handle `/your-command`, `/like`, `/magic`
- ğŸ’¬ **Event handling** â€” `@app_mention`, `message`, `reaction_added`, etc.
- ğŸ¨ **Slack formatting** â€” Clean markdown and block formatting made easy
- ğŸ§© **Plugin system** â€” Extend functionality with decorators and custom plugins
- âš™ï¸ **FastAPI + Slack SDK** â€” Built on proven tools, superfast and flexible

